<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2310/96 of 2 December 1996 amending Council Regulation (EEC) No 1101/89 in respect of the conditions applying to the placing in service of new pusher-craft capacity on inland waterways </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (E&Uuml;) nr 2310/96, millega muudetakse n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1101/89 siseveetranspordis t&otilde;ukurpuksiiride uue kandev&otilde;ime kasutuselev&otilde;tu suhtes kehtivate tingimuste osas 2. detsember 1996 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 1101/89 of 27 April 1989 on structural improvements in inland waterway transport (1), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 2819/95 (2), and in particular Article 8 (1) (c) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 27. aprilli 1989. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1101/89 siseveetranspordi struktuurilise t&otilde;hustamise kohta, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 2819/95, (2) eriti selle artikli 8 l&otilde;ike 1 punkti c, ning arvestades, et: </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas changes in the pusher-craft sector within the internal market for transport by inland waterway requires the 'old for new' ratio to be adjusted in order to facilitate the modernization of the equipment concerned for reasons of safety; whereas that ratio should therefore be adjusted by reducing it to 1: 1; </inglise>
<eesti> muudatuste t&otilde;ttu siseveetranspordituru t&otilde;ukurpuksiiride sektoris on vaja "vana uue asemel" h&uuml;vitiste suhet kohandada, et h&otilde;lbustada seadmete moderniseerimist ohutuse t&otilde;ttu; nimetatud suhet tuleks seet&otilde;ttu kohandada 1: 1; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the Member States have been consulted on the measure provided for by this Regulation, and whereas an opinion on this has been received from a panel of experts on structural improvements to the inland waterways as provided for by Article 12 of Commission Regulation No 1102/89 of 27 April 1989 laying down certain measures implementing Regulation No 1101/89 concerning structural improvements in inland waterway transporting (3), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 3039/94 (4), </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses s&auml;testatud meetme puhul on konsulteeritud liikmesriikidega ning oma arvamuse on esitanud siseveetranspordi struktuurilise t&otilde;hustamise eskpertide r&uuml;hm, nagu see on s&auml;testatud komisjoni 27. aprilli 1989. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1102/89 (3) (millega n&auml;hakse ette erimeetmed n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1101/89 (siseveetranspordi struktuurilise t&otilde;hustamise kohta) rakendamiseks, viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 3039/94 (4)) artiklis 12, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> Article 8 (1) (a) second indent of Regulation (EEC) No 1101/89 shall be amended as follows: </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1101/89 artikli 8 l&otilde;ike 1 punkti a teist taanet muudetakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise> 'In the case of pusher craft the term tonnage shall be replaced by that of motive power. </inglise>
<eesti> <hi rend="sub"> "</hi> T&otilde;ukurpuksiiride puhul asendatakse termin tonnaa&zcaron; terminga liikumapanev j&otilde;ud. </eesti>
<inglise> For this type of vessel the ratio between the motive power of a pusher craft that has recently been placed in service and that of a previous pusher craft that has been scrapped shall, by way of an exception from the first indent, be equivalent (1: 1). </inglise>
<eesti> Seda t&uuml;&uuml;pi laevade puhul on hiljuti kasutusele v&otilde;etud t&otilde;ukurpuksiiri ja eelmise lammutatud t&otilde;ukurpuksiiri liikumapaneva j&otilde;u suhe erandina esimesest taandest 1: 1." </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall take effect from the twentieth day following that of its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub kahek&uuml;mnendal p&auml;eval p&auml;rast selle avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 2 December 1996. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 2. detsember 1996 </eesti>
